OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy overnight with some patchy rain
OL,7,For drizzle returning, especially in
OL,8,Fthe west around coasts and hills.
OL,9,FFeeling warm and humid, with murky
OL,10,Fconditions continuing near coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAnother grey start, with
OL,13,Fpatchy drizzle towards the west. Skies
OL,14,Fwill brighten in the east, though many
OL,15,Fwestern areas holding onto lots of
OL,16,Fcloud. Feeling warm and muggy once
OL,17,Fagain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
