OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,6,Fweather in the east on Friday, staying
OL,7,Fcloudier further west with patchy
OL,8,Fdrizzle. Fresher on Saturday with
OL,9,Fbright spells then more sunshine on
OL,10,FSunday, and feeling hotter.
